BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:G5Zc9ExIgPMJpIxXM6H-F
SUMMARY:Jarv x RDGLDGRN  w/ Damn Skippy
DTSTAMP:20260327T072419Z
DTSTART:20260413T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $25 ($31.93 after fees)\n\nDay of: $30 ($37.08 after f
	ees)\n\nJarv:\n\nBrooklyn-based MC / Producer\, Jarv started making music 
	in 2009 and put out his first official release "Jarvage Vol.1" in 2016. He
	 has since released four full-length projects in his modern yet classic bo
	om-bap style. He has garnered millions of streams and YouTube views and ha
	s toured with the likes of RA The Rugged Man\, Masta Ace\, Little Stranger
	\, Mr. Lif & Akrobatik\, Sadat X\, Spose\, The Palmer Squares and so on.\n
	\nRDGLDGRN:\n\nRDGLDGRN have always been about the blending of worlds. Eve
	n their name stems from the merging of its member’s diverse influences and
	 personalities\, each represented by a corresponding color - Red (Guitar)\
	, Gold (Bass) and Green (Vocals). On LP3\, they’ve managedto set a new bar
	 for how contrasting sounds can come together. With that being said\, it’s
	 no surprise that it is also the record they’ve had the most control over.
	 After learning the many lessons of navigating the major label system over
	 the past six years\, the band will be releasing LP3 on their own label\, 
	Deuce Day World. It is an album that the band feels finally captures the i
	dea RDGLDGRN was based. “Everyone views us in a different way\,” Green add
	s\, “and in the past that has defined our music. On LP3\, the music captur
	es exactly how we see ourselves”.\n\nPlease note\, the Sunset Tavern is a 
	strictly 21+ bar and venue and does not accept vertical ID’s for entry.\n\
	nhttps://link.dice.fm/Yd8ce450ce91\n\nFrom Sunset Tavern
URL:https://link.dice.fm/Yd8ce450ce91
LOCATION:5433 Ballard Avenue Northwest\, Seattle\, Washington 98107\, Unite
	d States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:sunset-tavern
CATEGORIES:Sunset Tavern
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
